_sText:
3rd map made by me, GabrielPapaK. Has lots of teleports and secret places.

Features:

2 Bombsites
Maze where every corner is a hiding place
Many secret areas


Install:

Extract the map file (de_dust_mazes.bsp), and the navigation file (de_dust_mazes.nav) to your Counter-Strike maps folder (Usually located here:C:\Program Files\steam\steamapps\***YOURNAMEHERE***\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps).

Author: GabrielPapaK

Time: About 7 Hours.

Story: 
In this weird, in mysterious tunnel system, enemy forces have been identified. They have sworn to blow up some resources. Kill this terrorist group.
